---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Page">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-showcase"></div>
        <div class="about-description">
            <h1 class="about-description__heading">About</h1>
            <p class="about-description__text">
                <span
                    >The Reverie Group, incorporated in 2020 (RC1747218), came
                    into inception just at the end of COVID’s first bout as
                    lockdowns were being lifted with the resultant effect of
                    people & businesses retiring to a new world order of remote
                    working, masks & vaccines.</span
                >

                <span
                    >TRG was born on a guiding principle, to explore new real
                    estate frontiers, while creating savvy as well as tech
                    compliant standards with the unchanging mantra – our clients
                    remain the nucleus for all our activities.</span
                >

                <span
                    >As a customer-centric real estate brand, we’ve curated
                    bespoke services and processes, taking into cognizance the
                    uniqueness & individuality of every client. We also ensure
                    that our core values of integrity, creativity, excellence &
                    customer-centricity are firmly imprinted even on the
                    smallest tasks that we undertake.</span
                >
                <span>Welcome to a world of endless possibilities.</span>

                <span>Welcome to TRG</span>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-showcase"></div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .about-showcase {
        margin-top: 30px;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 450px;
        margin-left: 20px;
        vertical-align: middle;
        border-radius: 10px;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        background-image: url("../images/about-showcase-image.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        position: relative;
        border: none;
        outline: none;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
    }
    .about-description__heading {
        font-size: 3rem;
    }

    span {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
</style>
